    comment: '<p>The HTML <code>&#x3C;button></code> element may seem similar to a link <code>&#x3C;a></code> with a little more default style, but there are key differences:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Buttons are best used <em>within</em> Forms.</li>\n<li>Buttons not used within Forms require JavaScript to have any functionality.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The default <code>&#x3C;button></code> element looks like this:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-html">&#x3C;form action="/" method="post">\n  &#x3C;button>Submit&#x3C;/button>\n&#x3C;/form>\n</code></pre>\n<p><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="320" height="57"><g fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><rect width="320" height="57" fill="#FFF" rx="9"/><text fill="#000" font-family="ArialMT, Arial" font-size="11.5"><tspan x="27" y="32">Submit </tspan></text><rect width="50" height="17" x="19" y="20" stroke="#D9D9D9" rx="4"/></g></svg></p>\n<!--[View CodePen](https://codepen.io/enkidevs/pen/dKQxjM)--> \n<p>In this case, both the button and the input look and behave the same.</p>\n<pre><code class="language-html">&#x3C;form action="/" method="post">\n  &#x3C;button>Submit&#x3C;/button>\n  &#x3C;input type="submit">\n&#x3C;/form>\n</code></pre>\n<!--[View CodePen](https://codepen.io/enkidevs/pen/rryRQp)-->\n<p>The <code>&#x3C;button></code> element has a slight edge over the <code>&#x3C;input></code> as both images and text can be placed within it like this:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-html">&#x3C;button>\n  &#x3C;img src="submit-icon.svg" alt="">\n  Submit\n&#x3C;/button>\n</code></pre>\n<p><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="320" height="77"><defs><linearGradient id="a" x1="50%" x2="50%" y1="5.66906%" y2="96.75984%"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#E3E3E3"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#F7F7F7"/></linearGradient></defs><g fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><rect width="320" height="77" fill="#FFF" rx="9"/><path fill="url(#a)" stroke="#AFAFAF" d="M24 20h66c2.20914 0 4 1.79086 4 4v29c0 2.20914-1.79086 4-4 4H24c-2.20914 0-4-1.79086-4-4V24c0-2.20914 1.79086-4 4-4z"/><text fill="#000" font-family="ArialMT, Arial" font-size="11.5"><tspan x="60" y="52">Send </tspan></text><path fill="#000" fill-rule="nonzero" d="M42 22L27 33.25V52h30V33.25L42 22zm5.625 16.88783L42 43.30803l-5.625-4.4202V33.25h11.25v5.63783zm-10.52584 2.95348L28.875 48.8909V35.37953l8.22416 6.46178zM42 45.69203l3.39844-2.66965 8.2855 7.10262H30.31606l8.28645-7.10268L42 45.69203zm13.125-10.3125V48.8909l-8.22328-7.0496 8.22328-6.46177zm-.77637-1.77428L49.5 37.41566V31.375h-15v6.03879l-4.84863-3.8086L42 24.34376l12.34863 9.2615zM45.75 36.0625h-7.5v-.9375h7.5v.9375zm0 1.875h-7.5V37h7.5v.9375zm0 1.875h-7.5v-.9375h7.5v.9375z"/></g></svg></p>\n<!--[View CodePen](https://codepen.io/enkidevs/pen/VdqZdQ)-->\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Buttons have no default action upon click. This is why they are best tied to forms or advanced uses of JavaScript.</p>\n',
